{"tid":2356947,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英媒：「想贏選舉」成顛覆政權新定義","createTime":"2021-01-07T06:04:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T06:14:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"769fb736fb38f70a0124eacdaf8f846dbce80415","tid":2356947,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T06:04:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210107/GKEHWJA2YVC2JCNZXXFIRFLSNI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210107%2FGKEHWJA2YVC2JCNZXXFIRFLSNI%2F&d=tgCcTb3Ji4LFIEkqsM1g5lBOXtrJgaeu%2B3uDm9UxZFo%3D&h=bd48c8d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210107%2FGKEHWJA2YVC2JCNZXXFIRFLSNI%2F&h=e7380812\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210107/GKEHWJA2YVC2JCNZXXFIRFLSNI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n英媒：「想贏選舉」成顛覆政權新定義<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/amCasI-82gZr6YG2v1lCPMQ5dMs=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KB5RD3REKBC3XKLRJ2CXQBKKQQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FamCasI-82gZr6YG2v1lCPMQ5dMs%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKB5RD3REKBC3XKLRJ2CXQBKKQQ.jpg&h=28aa96a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■BBC昨報道大批民主派人士被捕時（圖），以「肅清反對派」（下圖）形容。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港警方昨拘捕53名民主派人士，指他們涉嫌違反港版國安法，惹來國際傳媒高度關注。英國天空新聞台亞洲新聞記者切希爾（Tom Cheshire）形容，中國政府以港版國安法拘捕民主派人士，「看似肅清多於執法」，批評當局單以民主派力爭立法會過半議席便拘捕他們，為顛覆政權立下「嶄新定義」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：國安歹毒：初選有罪  警拘戴耀廷53人<br />\n<br />\n切希爾指出，北京視港版國安法為「尚方寶劍」，但現時「看來更像大錘」，用以打壓民主派，這次也是港版國安法去年通過以來，最大規模、針對最知名人士的拘捕行動，被捕者涉及多個界別，警方亦搜查律師樓並要求新聞機構提交文件，「這看來更像是肅清，而非執法」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kJvIUjQq1pvR_i4k4Bdh2LD9Vj4=/1000x456/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4IIFHO6MDJBMXEIR7QBODQ3JNI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkJvIUjQq1pvR_i4k4Bdh2LD9Vj4%3D%2F1000x456%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4IIFHO6MDJBMXEIR7QBODQ3JNI.jpg&h=fbf8c9a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n切希爾進一步指，拘捕行動的「理據」較其規模更令人震驚，稱民主派人士被指涉嫌顛覆政權，原因是他們去年7月為準備立法會選舉，舉辦非官方初選，並希望在立法會取得過半議席，「這實在是顛覆政權的嶄新定義：想贏得選舉」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：多國政要轟打壓「拜登站港人一方」 歐盟促放人 制裁擬升級<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBBC：圖消滅反對陣營<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司（BBC）亦指，當局推行港版國安法時，聲稱只是針對極少數人，但昨天的拘捕行動範圍之廣，已令很多人憂慮政權正試圖消滅整個反對陣營。BBC形容港版國安法製造白色恐怖，不但街頭抗爭被噤聲，更有越來越多民主派人士流亡。<br />\n<br />\n美國有線新聞網絡（CNN）則指香港警方跟隨中聯辦去年7月對民主派初選的威嚇言詞，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hXnv9oKJh0aQ9UkDZm3Leontkpg=/1299x1122/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GR6DV42W3JEJLAIXE5L3V2BFWI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhXnv9oKJh0aQ9UkDZm3Leontkpg%3D%2F1299x1122%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGR6DV42W3JEJLAIXE5L3V2BFWI.gif&h=f56a58a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■日本《朝日新聞》（上圖）及英國《金融時報》（下圖）等海外媒體均有報道事件。"},{"pid":"6ad4d04c91dcbfa4b6b09b2061d88a05ee23a776","tid":2356947,"uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T06:14:14.000Z","msg":"中共滅聲唔駛你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}